 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/uycorerixle.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ycorerixle</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>New to the block</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(2/27/01 12:40:08 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.facelink.com/ycore?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60 WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A no brainer...</span><hr size=1> Actually, it's quite easy. CH is 10 seconds, and CoH is 12 seconds.  What I've done is have the cleric announce CH in guildchat, and immediately start casting CoH.  If the mob peels off the tank and makes a beeline for the cleric, he is summoned 2 seconds later with aggro cleared and the mob makes a 180 for the tank again.  If the mob stays on the tank, the mage just ducks and saves 500 mana and a 5pp pearl.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showMessage?topicID=95.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showMessage?topicID=87.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.emailToFriend?topicID=93.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.threadControl?topicID=93.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/grunge/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=93.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.unsubscribeUnregister